#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.125:0.2"
msgid "13. Gahapativagga "
msgstr "13. Householders "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 125. Vajjīsutta → vajji (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.125:0.3"
msgid "125. Vajjīsutta "
msgstr "125. In the Land of the Vajjis "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.110, sc1
msgctxt "sn35.125:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā vajjīsu viharati hatthigāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Vajjis at the village of Hatthi. "

msgctxt "sn35.125:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho uggo gahapati hatthigāmako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho uggo gahapati hatthigāmako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the householder Ugga of Hatthi went up to the Buddha, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.125:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme no parinibbāyanti? "
msgstr "“What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why some sentient beings aren’t fully extinguished in the present life? "

msgctxt "sn35.125:1.4"
msgid "Ko pana, bhante, hetu ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme parinibbāyantī”ti? "
msgstr "What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why some sentient beings are fully extinguished in the present life?” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.125:1.5"
msgid "(Yathā purimasuttantaṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.) "
msgstr "(This should be told in full as in the previous discourse.) "

msgctxt "sn35.125:1.6"
msgid "“Ayaṃ kho, gahapati, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme parinibbāyantī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.125:1.7"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

